Class CustomList<Type>

    • structures.CustomList<Type>
  • Type Parameters:
    Type - The Object type in the list
    public class CustomList<Type>
extends java.lang.Object
    A simple list with some core functionality. Table is the array in which the values are stored Length is the number of entries in the table AbsoluteSize is the size of the array
